title: [Rogue Guild, Courtyard Center]
description: The large statue in the center of an overgrown flowerbed was once the focal point of the courtyard.  Now, missing its head and one arm, and streaked with the indignities left by generations of birds inhabiting its various sheltering spaces, it stands as a bleak reminder that the days of elegance and affluence for this place are long over.
paths: Obvious paths: northeast, southeast, southwest, northwest
